WEBVTT

04:18.612 --> 04:28.012
Today we have gathered here to worship Shri Ganesha.

04:29.692 --> 04:37.012
You all know what a powerful deity He is.

04:37.172 --> 04:42.351
His power comes from his innocence.

04:42.511 --> 04:47.153
When we see small children we are automatically

04:47.313 --> 04:50.772
compelled towards them

04:50.932 --> 04:58.292
and also we want to love them, kiss them and be with them.

04:58.452 --> 05:03.212
And very innocent they are,

05:04.492 --> 05:06.812
extremely innocent,

05:06.972 --> 05:13.332
and when we worship Shri Ganesha

05:13.492 --> 05:20.292
we have to know if we have been really innocent or not.

05:20.492 --> 05:27.172
These days people have become extremely cunning,

05:27.332 --> 05:30.972
and they don’t mind any amount of cunning.

05:31.132 --> 05:34.532
They play all kinds of cunning games on others

05:34.692 --> 05:38.572
who are innocent and simple.

05:38.732 --> 05:41.972
They can justify themselves always

05:42.132 --> 05:47.052
that whatever they are doing is the right thing in these modern times

05:47.212 --> 05:50.332
when everybody is so cunning.

05:50.492 --> 06:00.572
This cunningness can take you to the other extreme of right side,

06:00.772 --> 06:03.892
which is very much punishable,

06:04.172 --> 06:09.732
in the sense that some people develop all kinds of problems,

06:09.892 --> 06:13.732
which are physical, you can say.

06:14.092 --> 06:22.052
Like their hands can get paralyzed or their leg can get paralyzed.

06:23.012 --> 06:26.252
Also, they can have other troubles

06:26.412 --> 06:29.932
with their liver treatments and all that.

06:30.092 --> 06:35.972
All this comes up. Then to punish them

06:36.132 --> 06:41.652
a disease of psychosomatic nature might set in.

06:41.892 --> 06:45.052
At this time, when you have these problems,

06:45.212 --> 06:48.452
all such people, who suffer from the right side,

06:48.612 --> 06:51.492
should worship Shri Ganesha.

06:51.732 --> 06:59.052
For example these days, life is very much busy with all of you.

06:59.212 --> 07:04.532
You are extremely busy with your work and you are doing

07:04.692 --> 07:08.732
extra work, I should say, than normal.

07:08.932 --> 07:13.452
But you think you are doing a very great job of God.

07:13.612 --> 07:17.892
As a result Shri Ganesha is neglected

07:18.052 --> 07:25.372
and such a man can become either very dry or very self indulgent.

07:25.532 --> 07:28.172
One of the two things come up

07:28.332 --> 07:32.492
and he does not know where he is going.

07:32.652 --> 07:38.692
The only thing that keeps you in the middle,

07:38.852 --> 07:43.332
in Sahaja Yoga, is Shri Ganesha’s Puja,

07:43.492 --> 07:50.692
Shri Ganesha’s worship by which you can always be in the center.

07:50.852 --> 07:54.049
All these diseases of the right side

07:54.209 --> 07:58.612
can be cured by Shri Ganesha’s Puja.

07:58.772 --> 08:04.572
Now there are various ways people worship Shri Ganesha

08:05.572 --> 08:12.012
but there is a simple way to remember him

08:12.172 --> 08:17.572
and sit before his photograph and take vibrations from him.

08:17.732 --> 08:21.492
That’s the best way you can balance yourself.

08:21.652 --> 08:26.412
There are so many worries, there are so many struggles you have.

08:26.572 --> 08:30.252
All these can be neutralized by Shri Ganesha.

08:30.452 --> 08:35.132
Though innocent, He is extremely clever

08:35.292 --> 08:39.972
and when he comes to your help you are amazed.

08:40.132 --> 08:44.932
How he works it out and how he removes all the hurdles

08:45.092 --> 08:47.612
and all the worries from you.

08:47.772 --> 08:51.692
So this is the most important deity we have.

08:51.852 --> 08:55.052
Though its a very simple deity.

08:55.212 --> 08:58.732
This Mooladhara chakra is very very complicated.

08:58.892 --> 09:02.092
It is one of the most complicated, chakras I think,

09:02.252 --> 09:10.772
because it has many waves, it has many compartments.

09:10.932 --> 09:17.772
We can say which all the time are vibrating and oscillating.

09:17.932 --> 09:20.652
So to steady down these

09:20.812 --> 09:27.852
you should try to be absolutely dedicated to Shri Ganesha.

09:28.092 --> 09:35.052
Shri Ganesha, as I told you, was incarnated as Jesus Christ,

09:35.252 --> 09:40.012
and Jesus was also a very innocent person.

09:40.172 --> 09:44.172
If he was not innocent, He would not have been crucified,

09:44.332 --> 09:48.492
but he was not a cunning fellow to see the cunning of others.

09:48.652 --> 09:53.892
His own disciple deceived him and still he knew who it was,

09:54.052 --> 09:56.012
he never said who it was.

09:56.172 --> 10:00.972
If you see his life, its full of innocent beauty,

10:01.132 --> 10:07.572
is such a simple hearted personality, such a good personality

10:07.732 --> 10:10.452
and wherever he saw anything wrong done

10:10.612 --> 10:13.292
he used to go all out to fight it.

10:13.452 --> 10:15.412
Same is Shri Ganesha.

10:15.572 --> 10:20.492
Shri Ganesha’s blessings are very important for all the people

10:20.652 --> 10:25.532
who are specially prone to some sort of a hurdle

10:25.692 --> 10:28.852
or ‘Sankata as they call it’. He is called as Sankata Vimochan,

10:29.012 --> 10:33.692
the one who takes you out of all the hurdles of life.

10:33.852 --> 10:38.132
So many of you have experienced how he has helped you

10:38.292 --> 10:42.892
in different troubles and hurdles and also

10:43.052 --> 10:46.532
different type of very very difficult times.

10:46.692 --> 10:51.132
It is his style that he manages things so well

10:51.292 --> 10:53.972
because he is a Ganapati.

10:54.132 --> 11:00.092
Ganapati means the one who is the Lord of the Ganas.

11:00.252 --> 11:04.852
As I have told you Ganas exist within us.

11:05.012 --> 11:13.012
Very nicely settled down as these bodies, small, small bodies

11:13.172 --> 11:17.092
who report if there is any problem.

11:17.252 --> 11:21.372
They report to the brain that there is a problem

11:21.532 --> 11:28.172
and on the sternum bone is the residence

11:28.332 --> 11:33.972
or you can say the throne of the Goddess Durga.

11:34.132 --> 11:42.972
So whenever there is any problem we are found into some trouble,

11:43.132 --> 11:46.692
sternum bone starts vibrating

11:46.852 --> 11:53.332
and these bodies which are Ganas get the information.

11:53.492 --> 11:57.492
Antibodies they are called in the medical terminology.

11:57.652 --> 12:02.612
Then these Ganas attack. They can target also.

12:02.772 --> 12:06.732
They know how to target the troubles and attack it,

12:06.892 --> 12:10.852
one may think that only the people who are suffering medically

12:11.012 --> 12:13.652
are helped by Ganas is not true.

12:13.812 --> 12:17.132
Also the people who are mentally upset,

12:17.292 --> 12:22.012
who are mentally suffering are also helped by the Ganas.

12:22.172 --> 12:27.292
These Ganas are so good at targeting their problems

12:27.452 --> 12:32.372
that sometimes we are surprised how things are worked out.

12:32.532 --> 12:39.012
For example say something happens to someone, some child, somewhere.

12:39.172 --> 12:43.812
Now his parents start crying for Mother

12:43.972 --> 12:47.932
and the Mother is the Durga say, then what happens,

12:48.092 --> 12:51.692
that they immediately rush to that place

12:51.852 --> 12:56.332
and miraculously they cure the boy, miraculously they say.

12:56.492 --> 13:00.092
So many miraculous thing that have happened in your life

13:00.252 --> 13:06.892
you cannot explain, but they are all due to this Ganapati’s Ganas.

13:07.052 --> 13:10.652
They are also small like him

13:10.812 --> 13:14.412
and they are very active and very alert.

13:14.572 --> 13:16.532
They never sleep.

13:16.692 --> 13:20.732
Anytime there is any trouble these Ganas will go

13:20.892 --> 13:25.732
and attack the problem and find out solution for him.

13:25.892 --> 13:32.052
It is something unbelievable how they act and how they inform.

13:32.812 --> 13:36.452
I can give you so many examples that have happened like this.

13:36.612 --> 13:40.772
For example there was a boy who got drowned

13:40.932 --> 13:47.172
in one of our ashrams in America in the swimming pool.

13:47.332 --> 13:49.252
They were all jumping in the swimming pool,

13:49.412 --> 13:51.972
I didn’t like the idea of swimming pool very much

13:52.132 --> 13:54.292
because there were children.

13:54.452 --> 13:57.012
So one boy fell down into that

13:57.172 --> 14:00.372
and was inside for about 15 to 20 minutes.

14:00.532 --> 14:02.492
Nobody knew he was there.

14:02.652 --> 14:08.172
So then they tried to find out the body of the boy

14:08.332 --> 14:11.892
and then they found out he was not there. Where has he gone?

14:12.052 --> 14:16.852
Then they discovered that he was in that swimming pool.

14:17.012 --> 14:20.532
After that they got so frightened

14:20.692 --> 14:24.292
and they said we just prayed to you, Mother to save this boy.

14:24.452 --> 14:26.972
Surprisingly, I never telephone to any Ashram,

14:27.132 --> 14:29.402
I didn’t know even the address.

14:29.562 --> 14:33.972
But I asked to telephone to this number,

14:34.132 --> 14:37.052
on my own. I don’t know anybody’s numbers

14:37.212 --> 14:42.812
and, when I telephoned, one of the leaders came there

14:42.972 --> 14:46.052
and I told him I know the boy has fallen into the water

14:46.212 --> 14:47.772
and he will be saved.

14:47.932 --> 14:49.932
Nobody had told me anything.

14:50.092 --> 14:52.692
“Don’t worry he will be perfectly alright.”

14:52.852 --> 14:57.532
Then they brought out the boy and he was treated

14:57.692 --> 15:01.572
by the doctors also but also with vibrations

15:01.732 --> 15:04.252
and today that boy is perfectly alright,

15:04.412 --> 15:07.292
while the doctors had said he can never survive.

15:07.452 --> 15:09.892
If there is one chance of his surviving,

15:10.052 --> 15:14.972
he will be like a dead body, in a coma all the time.

15:15.132 --> 15:18.092
This boy, I have met him this time, when I went to America.

15:18.252 --> 15:20.172
So, like this, so many things happen

15:20.332 --> 15:26.292
and people tell me that Mother its your ‘kripa’,

15:26.452 --> 15:29.892
your blessings that this has happened.

15:30.052 --> 15:32.892
In a way, it is very distantly, I should say,

15:33.052 --> 15:35.492
but because of Shri Ganesha.

15:35.652 --> 15:38.132
Now Shri Ganesha’s another quality is that

15:38.292 --> 15:41.652
he is extremely obedient to Mother.

15:41.812 --> 15:47.652
He does not recognize even Shiva, Vihnu, any one.

15:47.812 --> 15:51.252
To him his Mother is everything.

15:51.412 --> 15:54.412
So he can fight with his father, Shiva,

15:54.572 --> 16:00.092
he can fight with anyone because to him is complete obedience

16:00.252 --> 16:07.612
and absolutely quick ‘Tatpar’, just quickly understands

16:07.772 --> 16:12.372
what is the desire of the Mother and he works it out.

16:12.532 --> 16:17.932
His style is otherwise very innocent, simple, child like

16:18.092 --> 16:21.252
but His work is tremendous.

16:21.412 --> 16:26.132
Now these Ganas are also very innocent people, very innocent

16:26.292 --> 16:32.052
but when told that you have to attend to a particular problem,

16:32.212 --> 16:35.892
they are extremely quick and they are very fast.

16:36.052 --> 16:42.172
The another thing within is that he respects people who are chaste,

16:42.332 --> 16:46.852
who have chastity as the prime thing in their life.

16:47.012 --> 16:49.452
Chastity is very much worshipped by him.

16:49.612 --> 16:52.612
Its not only in women but also in men,

16:52.772 --> 16:55.932
he expects chastity to be present.

16:56.092 --> 17:01.292
After getting realization you should be absolutely chaste people,

17:01.452 --> 17:04.692
you shouldn’t have your eyes rolling around every where

17:04.852 --> 17:10.772
and sort of what you can call a very bad method

17:10.932 --> 17:15.092
of communicating with young women and young men

17:15.252 --> 17:18.012
and spoiling your chastity.

17:18.172 --> 17:21.012
Even your eyes should be clean,

17:21.172 --> 17:23.692
even your thoughts should be cleaned.

17:23.852 --> 17:27.772
For that you should introspect and see for yourself

17:27.932 --> 17:30.372
what mistakes you have committed

17:30.532 --> 17:37.372
and what kind of an unchaste behavior you have.

17:37.532 --> 17:42.812
You have to correct yourself and ask Shri Ganesha to forgive you.

17:42.972 --> 17:46.332
If you ask for forgiveness, he can forgive anything.

17:46.492 --> 17:50.732
He is so innocent and beautiful that he forgives you,

17:50.892 --> 17:53.532
but that is a very important thing.

17:53.692 --> 17:58.852
Our whole morality depends on our idea of chastity.

17:59.012 --> 18:00.572
We should be very chaste.

18:00.732 --> 18:04.772
So many religions have come and they have talked about chastity.

18:04.932 --> 18:08.572
But religions have become so useless now,

18:08.732 --> 18:12.012
have become without any basis,

18:12.172 --> 18:22.692
without any proper execution, of what is written for them.

18:22.852 --> 18:26.252
They do all kinds of things and they call themselves

18:26.412 --> 18:30.612
Hindus, Muslims, Christians, all kinds of religions.

18:30.772 --> 18:33.812
Actually the religions have failed completely

18:33.972 --> 18:38.812
and that’s why Shri Ganesha gets after them.

18:38.972 --> 18:41.092
Another thing about Shri Ganesh

18:41.252 --> 18:44.452
is that he is created out of the Mother earth.

18:44.612 --> 18:48.132
He is absolutely created out of the mother Earth.

18:48.292 --> 18:54.972
So if he doesn’t like people of some country,

18:55.132 --> 18:59.932
who are doing black magic, or who are doing fundamentalism

19:00.092 --> 19:06.692
and where people are also having very bad morals.

19:06.852 --> 19:11.492
He creates problems for them. What happens that

19:11.652 --> 19:18.532
He tells the Mother earth to create the earthquakes.

19:18.692 --> 19:21.076
Earthquake takes place in places where

19:21.236 --> 19:24.892
there is no respect of chastity,

19:25.052 --> 19:28.892
also where there are fundamentalist

19:29.052 --> 19:35.892
and also where there are people who are worshipping the black magic.

19:36.052 --> 19:40.812
This kind of people are attacked by him through his Mother.

19:40.972 --> 19:43.252
So the Mother earth also understands.

19:43.412 --> 19:46.852
Now we have so many earthquakes,

19:47.012 --> 19:49.292
one in Turkey you know, one in Taiwan,

19:49.452 --> 19:52.452
but not a single Sahaja Yogi has died.

19:52.612 --> 19:54.372
So he protects them.

19:54.532 --> 19:59.252
He has discrimination and only such people, who are of this kind,

19:59.412 --> 20:01.452
he tries to destroy them,

20:01.612 --> 20:05.572
and he has destroyed many like this even before.

20:05.732 --> 20:16.492
Also, the Mother earth’s powers he has got, is that he is magnetic,

20:16.652 --> 20:19.372
he attracts people towards himself,

20:19.532 --> 20:24.372
people take to him very easily as we take to children very easily.

20:24.532 --> 20:29.172
So that is magnetic power that he has got within himself.

20:29.332 --> 20:34.852
Now, you will be surprised this magnet exists also in the birds,

20:35.012 --> 20:38.052
also in many animals but specially in the birds.

20:38.212 --> 20:41.772
That’s how they can follow direction where they have to go.

20:41.932 --> 20:46.532
They are flying from, say Siberia, all the way, flying to Australia.

20:46.692 --> 20:50.252
How do they fly? And again they come back to the same place.

20:50.412 --> 20:56.932
It also is in the fishes. Fishes also are found say

20:57.092 --> 21:01.852
in the waters which are coming from some hills,

21:02.012 --> 21:06.412
so they come to the plains for some time and again God knows how,

21:06.572 --> 21:08.732
they go back to their own place.

21:08.892 --> 21:12.092
So going back to the same place is only possible

21:12.252 --> 21:15.092
if there is a way of knowing the direction.

21:15.252 --> 21:19.532
But they know the direction, they have a sense of direction,

21:19.692 --> 21:23.652
also they are bound by their own qualities.

21:23.812 --> 21:28.692
For example a snake will be a snake, a dog will be a dog,

21:28.852 --> 21:31.092
and a lion will be a lion.

21:31.252 --> 21:34.852
But human beings have perhaps all the animals within them.

21:35.012 --> 21:37.132
So they could be anything, you can’t say

21:37.292 --> 21:41.172
and they are too cunning to admit that they can be anything.

21:41.332 --> 21:43.932
And once they become anything like that

21:44.092 --> 21:48.692
you are amazed how these people can be of such a low level

21:48.852 --> 21:51.252
when they are human beings.

21:51.412 --> 21:56.012
But it is so because Ganesha has not been respected in their lives.

21:56.172 --> 22:01.092
So they can go to any level, any place. Another example,

22:01.252 --> 22:05.572
I give you a very big earthquake we had in India, in Latur.

22:05.732 --> 22:10.572
In Latur this was the fourteenth day of Shri Ganesha

22:10.732 --> 22:13.652
where they take Shri Ganesha and put it in the sea

22:13.812 --> 22:18.252
or in the water of a river. So there, in Latur,

22:18.412 --> 22:26.092
these people have been having a nice statue of Shri Ganesha.

22:26.252 --> 22:28.292
Before the statue they dance

22:28.452 --> 22:34.852
and they have now started playing very dirty, very bad,

22:35.012 --> 22:40.532
music from some very funny films or something.

22:40.692 --> 22:43.652
It’s so bad that you just can’t bear it.

22:43.812 --> 22:47.932
Very bad and that upsets Shri Ganesha.

22:48.092 --> 22:52.292
So like that they were doing to this one statue that they had

22:52.452 --> 22:54.732
and they were dancing before it.

22:54.892 --> 23:00.492
But when they put the statue in the water and they came back home,

23:00.652 --> 23:04.932
they got drunk and when they got drunk, they started dancing

23:05.092 --> 23:09.452
with that drinking and saying Jai Ganesha, Jai Ganesha.

23:09.612 --> 23:13.092
At that time the earth moved

23:13.252 --> 23:22.852
and the earthquake took away all of them inside the earth itself.

23:23.012 --> 23:25.332
They all disappeared into earth.

23:25.492 --> 23:28.652
Apart from that there were many others also

23:28.812 --> 23:33.052
who were doing this kind of thing, were taken into the mother earth.

23:33.212 --> 23:36.892
And our Ashram was there, a kind of a center

23:37.052 --> 23:44.652
and around the center there was a very beautiful land

23:44.812 --> 23:50.732
but he did not touch that land. Around is about at least

23:50.892 --> 23:56.012
quite a long distance, a big gap came in

23:56.172 --> 24:05.292
and there was a opening in the mother earth all around the center

24:05.452 --> 24:10.412
and nobody was harmed: They were all at home.

24:10.732 --> 24:12.892
They were all right.

24:13.052 --> 24:18.012
But this happened, that our Ashram was not at all touched

24:18.172 --> 24:20.688
and this is how they saved the Ashram

24:20.848 --> 24:23.652
and not a single Sahaja Yogi died.

24:23.812 --> 24:28.052
It is really very remarkable how the protection is given

24:28.212 --> 24:31.972
by Shri Ganesha and his Ganas.

24:32.132 --> 24:34.612
So we must respect his Ganas,

24:34.772 --> 24:39.372
very important is to see that they are all around within us,

24:39.532 --> 24:41.572
they are acting within us.

24:41.732 --> 24:44.892
They see us what sort of person you are,

24:45.052 --> 24:49.812
and in case you try to dislodge Shri Ganesha

24:49.972 --> 24:51.975
by your misbehavior

24:52.135 --> 24:56.412
they try to see that you again go back to normal.

24:56.572 --> 24:58.572
They give you a chance many a times.

24:58.732 --> 25:06.212
But even then you go on with your cunning and ideas about your ego,

25:06.372 --> 25:12.932
you are very badly hit by him and that is the biggest,

25:13.092 --> 25:17.012
I should say, calamity for you people.

25:17.172 --> 25:19.772
So you must worship Shri Ganesha

25:19.932 --> 25:23.172
but I always say don’t worship every Shri Ganesha

25:23.332 --> 25:28.732
which is being created by those, we can say, artisans.

25:28.892 --> 25:31.932
Because God knows what sort of Artisans they are.

25:32.092 --> 25:34.612
For money’s sake they might be making Ganesha

25:34.772 --> 25:41.172
and they might not have got any idea of Chastity.

25:41.332 --> 25:46.132
Such people make these Ganesha and then you worship those Ganeshas,

25:46.292 --> 25:49.012
so we are not at all helped by this.

25:49.172 --> 25:51.892
That’s why Mohammad Saheb has said,

25:52.052 --> 25:55.812
don’t do any worship of any idol

25:55.972 --> 25:59.692
because these idols have been created by human beings

25:59.852 --> 26:04.492
who are not authorized to do that. They are not Swayambhus.

26:04.652 --> 26:06.972
They are not created by the mother earth

26:07.132 --> 26:09.891
but are copied by people

26:10.051 --> 26:13.532
who are just wanting to make money out of them.

26:13.692 --> 26:17.332
So that’s, how any idol you get,

26:17.492 --> 26:23.612
say, from the shops need not be worshiped,

26:23.772 --> 26:26.972
it is not to be worshiped, any idol whatsoever.

26:27.132 --> 26:29.812
So whatever is not there,

26:29.972 --> 26:34.012
we should not worship because it is made by somebody

26:34.172 --> 26:37.612
who has very bad vibrations, who is a cheat,

26:37.772 --> 26:41.732
who is very cunning and thinks no end of himself.

26:41.892 --> 26:45.132
With such a person if you buy a Shri Ganesha

26:45.292 --> 26:48.172
it is going to harm you, is not going to help you.

26:48.332 --> 26:52.972
You can have it for decoration in the house but not for worship.

26:53.132 --> 26:57.012
There is no photograph of real Shri Ganesha, no photograph.

26:57.172 --> 27:03.492
There are eight Shri Ganeshas who came out of mother earth.

27:03.652 --> 27:08.892
I have seen them. But in those places the pujaris,

27:09.052 --> 27:13.172
the people who are the priest are horrible, horrible people.

27:13.332 --> 27:17.852
I went to one of them and he said, “I am getting Asthama”,

27:18.012 --> 27:22.772
“I am getting paralysis, how is it I am worshipping Shri Ganesha,

27:22.932 --> 27:25.972
my forefathers have worshipped Shri Ganesha

27:26.132 --> 27:29.172
and how he is doing this to us.”

27:29.332 --> 27:35.692
I said, you just introspect yourself, what kind of a life you lead,

27:35.852 --> 27:41.932
