how much it can hamper, or how much it can give you trouble,

28:11.172 --> 28:16.532
how much it can take you nearer to your death.

28:16.692 --> 28:21.772
He is so powerful, because all his energy is

28:21.932 --> 28:25.052
for the divine work of his Mother, all his energy.

