they make out of coconut. That’s what he eats.

28:43.452 --> 28:50.332
His body is so subtle and so, so powerful

28:50.492 --> 28:58.732
that he can move mountains after mountains.

28:58.892 --> 29:05.292
With his simplicity, with his sweetness, and with his innocence

29:05.452 --> 29:12.612
he can really change people. People who are very harsh,

29:12.772 --> 29:15.892
can be changed.

