If you see it from right side to left side,

30:31.372 --> 30:32.972
you see the Swastika,

30:33.132 --> 30:39.852
and if you see from down below upward then it looks like a Cross.

30:40.012 --> 30:45.212
So it proves that Shri Ganesha incarnated as Christ

30:45.372 --> 30:50.052
and he is the one who is worshipped all over the world,

30:50.212 --> 30:53.652
is already written in the Devi Mahatmayam if you read it,

30:53.812 --> 30:57.732
is all clearly written about him how he became an egg

30:57.892 --> 31:01.052
and out of the half of the egg became Christ

31:01.212 --> 31:05.812
and half of the egg was Shri Ganesha.

31:05.972 --> 31:10.012
All these things are there but we cannot understand it

31:10.172 --> 31:11.772
because we are confused.

31:11.932 --> 31:14.052
We don’t want to see it in a proper sense

31:14.212 --> 31:16.092
that this is already written there.

31:16.252 --> 31:21.692
So those who worship Christ, also worship Shri Ganesha

31:21.852 --> 31:29.092
and whatever you say to Christ you are saying it to Shri Ganesha.

31:29.252 --> 31:35.372
They are not two, they are one and absolutely one with each other.

31:35.532 --> 31:38.372
All the things I have told you about Christ,

31:38.532 --> 31:44.852
you can try to find out and you will prove it.

31:45.012 --> 31:48.012
Like Christ had these two fingers,

31:48.172 --> 31:52.492
this means one finger is for the Vishudhi as we say Shri Krishna

31:52.652 --> 31:57.132
and this one is Vishnu’s means this is his father’s.

31:57.292 --> 32:01.012
That means his father was Vishnu or Shri Krishna.

32:01.172 --> 32:04.692
Very clearly he used to do, why didn’t he use other fingers,

32:04.852 --> 32:07.452
only these two fingers why did he use.

32:07.612 --> 32:10.277
Pointing out towards his father

32:10.437 --> 32:14.352
who was Shri Vishnu and Shri Krishna.

32:14.692 --> 32:17.932
It is easy to understand what I am saying,

32:18.092 --> 32:21.412
if you see the vibrations of Shri Ganesha.

32:21.572 --> 32:28.252
If you see his vibrations and think of him you will be amazed,

32:28.412 --> 32:33.812
that your Agnya will open out, you will become thoughtless,

32:33.972 --> 32:37.972
because he is the Jesus and he is on the Agnya.

32:38.132 --> 32:39.908
So it all opens out

32:40.068 --> 32:45.484
and all the stupid ideas about wrecking the Agnya,

32:45.652 --> 32:49.612
this and that is all neutralized because you see for yourself,

32:49.772 --> 32:54.892
just the name of Shri Ganesha can open your Agnya.

32:55.052 --> 32:59.052
The cunningness that comes from Agnya is absolutely finished.

32:59.212 --> 33:01.012
You are no more cunning.

33:01.172 --> 33:07.732
When you see this innocence on your forehead,

33:07.892 --> 33:12.972
you are amazed at yourself and all such ideas just disappear.

33:13.132 --> 33:18.132
You cannot think of something very cunning and harmful to others.

33:18.292 --> 33:25.092
You are completely changed when the Agnya is absolutely opened out.

33:25.252 --> 33:29.972
This one is a very big blessing to us that we all have

33:30.132 --> 33:34.332
this Muladhara Chakra now put into proper thing.

33:34.492 --> 33:37.532
When you sit on the ground also it helps more

33:37.692 --> 33:43.743
because the mother of Shri Ganesha

33:43.903 --> 33:47.663
is this Prithvi, is this earth, the mother earth

33:47.823 --> 33:51.252
and that’s why we should look after the mother earth.

33:51.412 --> 33:53.412
We don’t look after the mother earth.

33:53.572 --> 33:56.892
We don’t understand the value of mother earth.

33:57.052 --> 34:01.012
Actually in Indian culture it is that

34:01.172 --> 34:04.172
when you are getting up in the morning,

34:04.332 --> 34:09.252
you must say Namaskar to the Mother earth

34:09.412 --> 34:13.692
because saying that I bow to you, O, Mother earth

34:13.852 --> 34:16.932
because I am touching you with my feet.

34:17.092 --> 34:19.412
Such respect you should have for Mother earth,

34:19.572 --> 34:21.292
then you won’t exploit it,

34:21.452 --> 34:25.052
you won’t have today’s problems of pollution and this and that.

34:25.212 --> 34:28.052
It all comes out of our ignorance

34:28.212 --> 34:32.612
that the Mother earth is the mother of Shri Ganesha

34:32.772 --> 34:36.452
who’s chakra we have got as Mooladhara.

34:36.612 --> 34:41.092
If you understand this you will be able to understand,

34:41.252 --> 34:44.172
what is to be done.

34:44.332 --> 34:47.252
The mother earth itself we should look after,

34:47.412 --> 34:51.012
we can glorify her, we can beautify her,

34:51.172 --> 34:53.412
we can do all kinds of things

34:53.572 --> 34:59.092
but the way we are exploiting the mother earth is a wrong idea,

34:59.252 --> 35:03.932
is very wrong because it is harming us with pollution.

35:04.092 --> 35:07.172
To cut down the trees, to cut down every thing

35:07.332 --> 35:11.892
that mother has produced and just to use it for money

35:12.052 --> 35:13.932
is a very wrong thing.

35:14.092 --> 35:17.692
One should think about it and when you cut one tree also

35:17.852 --> 35:19.852
you should put another one there.

35:20.012 --> 35:23.372
That is the beauty of the Mother earth,

35:23.532 --> 35:27.972
all the greenery, every thing is the beauty of the Mother earth.

35:28.132 --> 35:35.572
Many people have no interest in gardening or in nature, no interest.

35:35.732 --> 35:38.932
I don’t know how they live but they do

35:39.092 --> 35:45.092
without taking any interest in gardening or in the nature.

35:45.252 --> 35:49.132
Nature is so beautiful, just look at the nature,

35:49.292 --> 35:55.172
it is never smelling, is never dirty, every leaf is so organized

35:55.332 --> 35:58.332
that it should get the sunrays.

35:58.492 --> 36:00.052
There is no quarrel about it.

36:00.212 --> 36:03.852
They are so well organized, everything is so beautiful

36:04.012 --> 36:09.132
and it is never destroyed also by any animals. You will be amazed.

36:09.292 --> 36:11.492
The animals also don’t destroy,

36:11.652 --> 36:14.692
at the most they might eat some grass or something,

36:14.852 --> 36:18.532
but normally animals do not destroy any tree,

36:18.692 --> 36:21.172
do not destroy anything

36:21.332 --> 36:27.212
as we destroy the Mother earth for our own use.

36:27.372 --> 36:30.492
Whatever may be the cry for this,

36:30.652 --> 36:34.412
we have to understand that we have to respect to the Mother earth.

36:34.572 --> 36:37.412
Mother earth is the mother of Shri Ganesha,

36:37.572 --> 36:41.532
who is our, you should say the eldest Sahaja Yogi.

36:41.692 --> 36:46.532
He never had to take to yoga but he is in Yoga all the time.

36:46.692 --> 36:49.092
He is the greatest yogi we have

36:49.252 --> 36:52.692
and the way he is doing right things all the time.

36:52.852 --> 36:58.972
He never does anything wrong, never and he is so capable

36:59.132 --> 37:07.492
of getting to the position of any great deity that is possible,

37:07.652 --> 37:10.372
I would say. He is the greatest deity we have

37:10.532 --> 37:12.492
and we should really worship him.

37:12.652 --> 37:15.302
Through him all deities are worshiped

37:15.462 --> 37:22.692
and are made happy and blissful.

37:22.852 --> 37:28.332
So this is today’s thing was that I was just thinking that

37:28.492 --> 37:33.612
nowadays, in modern times how we have become shameless,

37:33.772 --> 37:44.892
how we have tried to trouble our chastity, for kind of a honor.

37:45.052 --> 37:49.532
If we have any honor you will have the chastity

37:49.692 --> 37:52.692
but you are dishonoring yourself

37:52.852 --> 37:56.292
and you think you have been very very smart and modern

37:56.452 --> 38:02.132
by becoming so sinful.

38:02.292 --> 38:05.772
All the sinful act that is going on in these modern times

38:05.932 --> 38:12.172
is absolutely wrong and it should be completely, we should abhor it.

38:12.332 --> 38:15.812
You should go no way near because that’s all wrong

38:15.972 --> 38:19.492
and that’s how Shri Ganesha gets angry.

38:19.652 --> 38:23.572
Decency is very important in understanding,

38:23.732 --> 38:29.732
what is our important basis, is our chastity.

38:29.892 --> 38:36.252
In India you know thirty two thousand women got themselves burnt

38:36.412 --> 38:40.492
for saving their chastity. I come from the same family

38:40.652 --> 38:44.412
and you can imagine what courage they must be having,

38:44.572 --> 38:48.810
what faith they must be having, in their chastity

38:48.970 --> 38:52.645
that if we lose our chastity what’s the use of our life.

38:52.805 --> 38:58.581
So they cared for their chastity, have done so much sacrifice

38:58.741 --> 39:03.132
to show that chastity is the most important thing, we all should have.

39:03.292 --> 39:08.035
Its not only for women but also for men, very much more for men.

39:08.195 --> 39:10.423
Shri Ganesha is very important thing

39:10.583 --> 39:13.045
because men can develop so many diseases

39:13.205 --> 39:16.853
if they do not respect Shri Ganesha.

39:17.694 --> 39:24.749
Our health would be the best if we look after Shri Ganesha

39:24.909 --> 39:28.108
because he is all the time repairing our body.

39:28.268 --> 39:31.953
He is all the time looking after, protecting us

39:32.113 --> 39:37.964
and our Shri Ganesha is in the Mooladhara.

39:38.124 --> 39:40.877
He is the one who is looking after our Kundalini,

39:41.037 --> 39:43.412
he is protecting our Kundalini.

39:43.572 --> 39:50.151
If any thing happens to us the Kundalini comes up

39:50.311 --> 39:55.909
but the one who supports her and, keeps her up,

39:56.069 --> 40:00.353
awakened and standing is Shri Ganesha. He works it out.

40:00.513 --> 40:04.532
He is the one who is the protector of our Kundalini

40:04.692 --> 40:11.553
which is also a basis of your self realization.

40:11.713 --> 40:15.151
So how much important is Shri Ganesha you should know,

40:15.311 --> 40:18.088
and you should find out about yourself,

40:18.248 --> 40:22.867
introspect that are we really dedicated to Shri Ganesha?

40:23.027 --> 40:25.412
If we are; what are we doing about it?

40:25.572 --> 40:31.753
Then you will develop a real hatred for all these dirty things.

40:31.913 --> 40:34.675
You will not like them, will not like such people.

40:34.835 --> 40:37.957
That is how a Sahaja Yogi should work it out.

40:38.117 --> 40:41.031
The children are the best as we know.

40:41.191 --> 40:48.618
Children are so sweet and so kind, they are so loving, so beautiful.

40:48.778 --> 40:52.993
In the same way we should know Shri Ganesha is there.

40:53.153 --> 40:56.488
He is the one who is really innocent

40:56.648 --> 41:00.896
but extremely, protective of you,

41:01.056 --> 41:04.530
very much protective, with his innocence.

41:04.690 --> 41:07.266
So we should also try to cherish our innocence

41:07.426 --> 41:11.172
and not to feel hurt because sometime such people are cheated,

41:11.332 --> 41:14.016
dominated, every thing happens, doesn’t matter.

41:14.176 --> 41:17.466
They will all suffer who will dominate innocent people.

41:17.626 --> 41:22.687
As the whole world, you see, there is a big uproar about it,

41:22.847 --> 41:25.012
people are talking about it that

41:25.172 --> 41:29.236
there should not be domination of the innocent simple people.

41:29.396 --> 41:32.591
It has happened but it all has to be changed,

41:32.751 --> 41:39.532
has to be brought to some last end otherwise people can not exist,

41:39.692 --> 41:44.250
like everywhere they went and oppressed so many people.

41:44.410 --> 41:48.060
In America, I was surprised to see that

41:48.220 --> 41:50.972
there were so many Red Indians,

41:51.132 --> 41:54.972
who are called as Indian Americans.

41:55.132 --> 42:00.259
They were all oppressed so much that they had to run away

42:00.419 --> 42:04.570
to different places and then I went to this place Canajoharie.

42:04.730 --> 42:07.372
I found the vibrations were so good.

42:07.532 --> 42:10.172
That means they were very innocent, simple people

42:10.332 --> 42:13.351
and Americans that time, who went there,

42:13.511 --> 42:16.372
tried to completely finish them.

42:16.532 --> 42:19.861
So they went and hid in places like Canajoharie

42:20.021 --> 42:23.612
but the Canajoharie has such tremendous vibrations

42:23.772 --> 42:26.622
that I said look at this, so many years have passed,

42:26.782 --> 42:30.492
still the people who live there or worked about

42:30.652 --> 42:35.793
and were absolutely enjoying this place were Red Indians,

42:35.953 --> 42:40.526
the ones who were Indians, we call them American Indians.

42:40.686 --> 42:42.861
But they are so simple and innocent

42:43.021 --> 42:45.972
and they were so, I think, spiritual people

42:46.132 --> 42:48.772
because they used to worship the Mother.

42:48.932 --> 42:51.572
All the time they worship the Mother.

42:51.732 --> 42:55.332
Even I have seen in other countries it has happened

42:55.492 --> 43:00.592
but I was happy to see that in Australia they are very secular.

43:00.752 --> 43:03.552
They have many Maoris and all those people

43:03.712 --> 43:05.432
and they encourage all of them

43:05.592 --> 43:09.432
and its so surprising that they have so much talent

43:09.592 --> 43:16.675
and they are bringing them to this state to show

43:16.841 --> 43:21.548
that they are equal in their rights, political rights, in Australia.

43:21.708 --> 43:23.912
Its a very good venture.

43:24.072 --> 43:30.792
Now this Ganesha has appeared in Australia is as Uluru,

43:30.952 --> 43:35.611
is a very big mountain which looks like Shri Ganesha.

43:35.771 --> 43:40.690
It has also a very big trunk, going down.

43:40.850 --> 43:44.952
Vibrations itself will prove that it is Shri Ganesha,

43:45.112 --> 43:46.352
from the mother earth.

43:46.512 --> 43:50.272
He has appeared in many places, Shri Ganesha not only there.

43:50.432 --> 43:57.592
But there I felt is really the source, source of vibrations.

43:57.752 --> 43:59.388
That’s what it is.

43:59.548 --> 44:04.228
And in Australia I thank him that because of him only

44:04.388 --> 44:07.952
Sahaja Yoga has worked so well and so easily,

44:08.112 --> 44:10.453
and Government also has never troubled us

44:10.613 --> 44:13.068
or there has been no problem with them.

44:13.228 --> 44:15.773
I don’t know what’s this helping them

44:15.933 --> 44:20.293
but perhaps it is Shri Ganesha as Uluru

44:20.453 --> 44:24.742
which is protecting Sahaja Yoga there and is growing so much.

44:24.902 --> 44:28.793
In the same way every where, wherever you may be

44:28.953 --> 44:31.043
Shri Ganesha should be worshipped

44:31.203 --> 44:35.447
and you will be helped out and out miraculously.

44:35.607 --> 44:37.731
You will be helped, miraculously

44:37.891 --> 44:43.102
but first do something about our chastity which is Shri Ganesha.

44:43.300 --> 44:45.125
